com.bmc.arsys.apitransport.chunking

Class ARChunkProcessorBase

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.bmc.arsys.apitransport.chunking.ARChunkProcessorBase
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IARChunkable
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    ARChunkImport, ARChunkReceiveProcessor, ARChunkSendProcessor, ARChunkSetCreateSupportFile

    public abstract class ARChunkProcessorBase
extends Object
implements IARChunkable
    Base class for chunking processor If caller need reserve any object among chunking calls other than chunking process internal reserved objects, caller can use ApiThreadLocalStorageBlock.setInternalChunkingObj(), which is available among all chunks and thread safe.
